<title>LATVIA: HANSABANK-LATVIJA STARTS PROPERTY LOAN OFFER.</title>
<headline>HANSABANK-LATVIJA STARTS PROPERTY LOAN OFFER.</headline>
<dateline>RIGA 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hansabank-Latvija said on Tuesday that it has launched a new loan scheme for people buying property.</p>
<p>The bank said in a statement that the repayment period is 10 years and the loan amount will start from $8,000 and will be lent for up to 60 percent of the property's market value.</p>
<p>The client has to have an account with the bank and no more tha 30 percent of the person's monthly salary can be allowed to repay the loan.</p>
<p>-- Riga Newsroom, +371 721 5240</p>
